{"type":"message","id":"e2691bc2","parentId":"dfcdc2aa","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:26:38.627Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-13 15:26:33 GMT+8] Feishu[tts] DM | ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 [msg:om_x100b52fde4454c84c323d74cfce3b46]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52fde4454c84c323d74cfce3b46\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-13 15:26 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\n我看了你的分析，1688 skill在这个流程里边不是那么的重要吗？"}],"timestamp":1776065198625}}
{"type":"message","id":"7e546e3f","parentId":"e2691bc2","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:27:09.246Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking whether 1688 skill is really that important in this workflow. Let me think about this...\n\nLooking at the overall workflow:\n1. Data sources: TikTok backend, third-party data platforms, Google Trends, 1688\n2. Scoring/filtering: AI model\n3. Output: Bitable\n\nFor 1688 specifically, we need to:\n- Search for products matching the TikTok product\n- Get: price, supplier rating, sales volume, weight\n- Find the same or similar product on 1688\n\nThe user is questioning whether investing in a 1688 skill is worth it. Let me think about what 1688 data we actually need:\n\n1. 1688 price (CNY) - to calculate profit margin\n2. Supplier score/rating - to assess supplier reliability\n3. Minimum order quantity (MOQ)\n4. Product weight - for shipping cost calculation\n5. Supplier name/address - for sourcing\n\nIs there a 1688 skill available in clawhub? Let me check.\n\nActually, looking at the available skills listed, I don't see a 1688-specific skill. The user mentioned \"1688官方有skills\" - perhaps they saw something about this. \n\nBut let me think practically: What would a 1688 skill do that VibeSurf browser automation can't?\n- 1688 product pages are just HTML - VibeSurf can crawl/scrape them\n- The data we need (price, supplier info, weight) is visible on the page\n\nSo actually, VibeSurf browser automation might be sufficient for 1688. A dedicated 1688 skill would be nice-to-have but not essential if the browser automation works well.\n\nThe user has a point - maybe we don't need a dedicated 1688 skill if VibeSurf can handle it. The key question is: does VibeSurf work well enough for 1688? That's what we need to verify.\n\n\nI should clarify what we actually need from 1688 and whether browser automation would handle it adequately."},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 你的质疑有道理。让我诚实评估一下：\n\n---\n\n## 1688 在流程中的实际作用\n\n我们从 1688 需要获取的数据：\n- **采购价**（CNY）→ 算利润必须\n- **供应商评分** → 货源可靠性\n- **商品重量** → 算头程运费\n- **同类货源排行** → 找更多供应商\n\n---\n\n## 1688 Skill vs VibeSurf 对比\n\n| 维度 | 1688 Skill（如果有） | VibeSurf 浏览器 |\n|------|----------------------|----------------|\n| 稳定性 | 可能更高（官方适配） | 依赖页面结构 |\n| 覆盖范围 | 受 Skill 功能限制 | 任意 1688 页面 |\n| 开发成本 | 需要找/开发 Skill | 直接可用 |\n| 维护成本 | 1688 改版需更新 | 同样需要维护 |\n\n---\n\n## 诚实结论\n\n**1688 Skill 不是必须的**。如果 VibeSurf 能稳定抓取 1688 数据（价格、供应商、重量），就能满足需求。\n\n1688 Skill 的价值在于\"更稳定\"，但**不是这个流程的瓶颈**。\n\n真正的瓶颈是：\n1. TK 后台 / 第三方平台（无 API，必须浏览器）\n2. 评分逻辑的准确性\n\n---\n\n**要不要我先用 VibeSurf 实际抓一个 1688 页面试试，看看数据提取的稳定性和难度？** 这样我们就能判断 Skill 是否真的必要。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776065198627,"responseId":"062bcdaf9f435b775dc35e2091abf06f"}}
