{"type":"message","id":"62dcb16d","parentId":"c849751f","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:32:45.639Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is pointing me to https://clawhub.1688.com/ as the official 1688 skill website. This is interesting - they mentioned 1688 has a skill. Let me check if this is a valid URL and what skills are available there.\n\nWait, clawhub.ai is the OpenClaw skill marketplace. Is the user saying that 1688 has skills on clawhub? Or is this a 1688-specific skill site?\n\nActually, looking at the URL again: `https://clawhub.1688.com/` - this looks like it could be a 1688-themed site on clawhub, or it could be a mistake. Let me try to fetch this URL to see what's there.\n\nActually, I should note that ClawHub (clawhub.ai) is the skill marketplace for OpenClaw. The URL `clawhub.1688.com` doesn't make sense as a separate skill marketplace. It's more likely the user is pointing me to a 1688 page or they made a typo.\n\nBut regardless, the user is saying 1688 has official skills. Let me search or check what's available. Actually, I should read the vibesurf skill reference for workflows since the user mentioned VibeSurf supports workflows.\n\nLet me focus on the user's main question: Can we create a VibeSurf workflow for the Vietnam market product selection SOP?\n\nThe answer is yes - VibeSurf supports workflows (execute_workflow). If the SOP is fixed, we can:\n1. Create a workflow in VibeSurf that automates the browser steps\n2. This would reduce token usage (no need for me to manually orchestrate each step)\n3. Scale it up for multiple products\n\nLet me read the VibeSurf workflows reference to understand how to set this up."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q4nzwx3kwpav_1","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://clawhub.1688.com/","maxChars":5000}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q4nzwx3kwpav_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/skills/vibesurf/references/workflows.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776065544418,"responseId":"062bcf08cbef1406b901783fe534a851"}}
