{"type":"message","id":"c60c8eb5","parentId":"8847e063","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:33:48.023Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-13 15:33:44 GMT+8] Feishu[tts] DM | ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 [msg:om_x100b52fd8bb940a4c383d33fcb21ee2]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52fd8bb940a4c383d33fcb21ee2\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-13 15:33 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\n关于刚刚我说的那个，就是流程优化好了之后，这个workflow是不是可以写到vibe surf的这个浏览器里边。这样，每次你只需要给他命令，然后返回来，在web surf里边也有你的API"}],"timestamp":1776065628021}}
{"type":"message","id":"0532e13b","parentId":"c60c8eb5","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:34:06.486Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about VibeSurf's API - they want to confirm that after we optimize the workflow/SOP, we can save it as a VibeSurf workflow, and then trigger it via API. They're pointing out that VibeSurf also has an API.\n\nThis is correct - VibeSurf supports workflows that can be executed via its API. Let me confirm this and explain how it would work.\n\nFrom the SKILL.md I read, VibeSurf has:\n- `execute_workflow` action\n- `search_workflows` action\n- `get_workflow_params` action\n\nAnd the user is correct - once a workflow is created in VibeSurf, it can be triggered via API calls, which would:\n1. Reduce token consumption (no need for the AI to plan steps each time)\n2. Speed up execution (workflow runs automatically)\n3. Allow scaling (batch process multiple products)\n\nLet me confirm this understanding and explain the architecture."},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 对，你理解得完全正确！\n\n---\n\n## VibeSurf Workflow 的实际工作方式\n\n```\n你给我命令（触发 Workflow）\n    ↓\n我调用 VibeSurf API → 执行已保存的 Workflow\n    ↓\nWorkflow 自动串联浏览器操作\n    ↓\n返回结构化结果给我\n    ↓\n我进行评分分析\n    ↓\n写入 Bitable / 通知你\n```\n\n**你只需要描述目标，剩下的自动执行。**\n\n---\n\n## 关键优势：Scale\n\nWorkflow 固化后，**输入可以是批量商品**：\n\n```\n单商品模式：\n  输入：1个商品链接 → 输出：1条评估结果\n\n批量模式（Scale）：\n  输入：100个商品链接 → 输出：100条评估结果 + 排序\n```\n\n---\n\n## Workflow 复用场景\n\n| 触发方式 | 说明 |\n|----------|------|\n| **让我执行** | 你说\"跑一遍越南市场\"，我调 API |\n| **定时触发** | 每天 9:00 自动跑（VibeSurf Schedule） |\n| **飞书消息触发** | 你发商品链接，我自动跑流程 |\n\n---\n\n## 下一步：先验证 Workflow 可行性\n\n现在需要确认一件事：**VibeSurf 是否正常运行？**\n\n要我现在调一下它的状态，确认连接正常？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776065628023,"response