{"type":"message","id":"b932f27b","parentId":"dc364894","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:37:50.029Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户发了两个重要信息：\n1. 一张图：1688官方Skills，包含12个API驱动的模块，包括 1688-product-search, inquiry-1688 等\n2. 一个链接：https://seller.tiktokshopglobalselling.com/product/opportunity - 这是TikTok Shop的商品机会页面\n\n这说明：\n1. 1688确实有官方Skills可用，而且有 product-search 这样的功能\n2. TK后台有商品机会页面，这是我们数据源之一\n\n现在我需要：\n1. 确认VibeSurf状态\n2. 考虑是否要整合1688官方Skill（通过VibeSurf的MCP配置）\n\n让我先确认VibeSurf是否正常运行，然后看看怎么整合这些信息。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g77pejex3xg2_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s $VIBESURF_ENDPOINT/health || echo \"VIBESURF_ENDPOINT not set, trying default\" && curl -s http://127.0.0.1:9335/health"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776065852357,"responseId":"062bd03c357458f5043add0a26aeb353"}}
