205]<svg /> <!-- SVG content collapsed -->\\n|SHADOW(open)|[16123]<input placeholder=请输入你的手机号 type=tel autocomplete=off name=mobile id=TikTok_Ads_SSO_Login_Mobile_Input />\\n[16096]<span id=TikTok_Ads_SSO_Login_Email_Panel_Button />\\n\\t使用邮箱登录\\n密码\\n|SHADOW(open)|[16135]<input placeholder=请输入您的密码 type=password autocomplete=new-password id=TikTok_Ads_SSO_Login_Pwd_Input />\\n[16137]<i id=TikTok_Ads_SSO_Login_Pwd_Icon />\\n[16154]<a id=TikTok_Ads_SSO_Login_FPwd_Btn />\\n\\t忘记密码？\\n[16158]<a id=TikTok_Ads_SSO_Login_Go_Code_Btn />\\n\\t使用验证码登录\\n[16172]<button name=loginBtn id=TikTok_Ads_SSO_Login_Btn />\\n\\t登录\\n还没有 TikTok Shop 账号？\\n[16011]<div />\\n\\t[16009]<div />\\n\\t\\t[16008]<div />\\n\\t\\t\\t[16007]<button />\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t立即注册\\n|SCROLL|<iframe /> (scroll)\\n\\t[26661]<div />\\n```\\n\\n\",\"error\":null,\"file_system_base_dir\":\"/data/vibesurf_workspace/apis\"},\"error\":null}","name":"sleep 3"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776065908370}}
{"type":"message","id":"613228a9","parentId":"f5797308","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:38:43.928Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The TK Seller backend is requiring login. This means we can't directly access it without authentication. This is a key constraint - the TikTok Seller backend requires login, and likely has anti-bot measures.\n\nThis tells me:\n1. TK Seller后台需要登录 - 我们的AI无法直接自动登录（需要短信验证码等）\n2. 这是一个需要人工介入的环节\n\nSo the workflow for TK data would need to be:\n- Option 1: User logs in manually once, we save session cookies\n- Option 2: Use the third-party data platforms (EchoTik, etc.) instead\n- Option 3: User provides the data manually\n\nLet me inform HALEI about this finding and the implications for the workflow architecture."},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 重要发现：TK Seller 后台**需要登录**，AI 无法自动完成登录（需要手机/邮箱验证码）。\n\n---\n\n## 各数据源的可自动化程度\n\n| 数据源 | 可自动化？ | 原因 |\n|--------|-----------|------|\n| **TK Seller 后台** | ⚠️ 受限 | 需要登录验证码，AI无法自动登录 |\n| **1688** | ✅ 可以 | 有官方 Skill + 公开页面 |\n| **第三方数据平台**（EchoTik等） | ✅ 可以 | 浏览器直接访问 |\n| **Google Trends** | ✅ 可以 | 公开页面 |\n| **飞书 Bitable** | ✅ 可以 | Skill 直连 |\n\n---\n\n## 建议的绕过方案\n\nTK 后台这块，有几个选择：\n\n1. **手动导出** → 你登录后导出CSV，我来分析\n2. **第三方平台** → EchoTik / InfluTalk（已有 API 思路）\n3. **TK 联盟后台** → 公开数据，不需要登录\n\n---\n\n**你觉得哪个方式更适合？** 或者你有 TK 的cookie/session 可以给我，让我维持登录状态？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776065908372,"responseId":"062bd07427cada139cf3a35ed8bf5039"}}
