{"type":"message","id":"5374ac1b","parentId":"425951d5","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:40:09.264Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Same result - still redirected to login page. The TK Seller后台需要登录才能访问任何数据页面。\n\nLet me think about what the user is really trying to do. They've been talking about:\n1. Getting product data from TK Shop\n2. Cross-referencing with 1688 for sourcing\n3. Using VibeSurf for browser automation\n4. Eventually creating workflows\n\nThe issue is that TK Seller后台 requires login. But there might be public-facing TK data that doesn't require login:\n- TikTok Shop public product pages\n- TikTok trending products (public)\n\nLet me suggest trying the public TikTok Shop product pages instead of the seller后台.\n\nActually, wait - the user shared the \"product opportunity\" page and the \"top selling\" page. These are inside the Seller Center, which definitely requires login. \n\nBut maybe they have a session/cookie they can share? Or maybe we should try a different approach altogether.\n\nLet me inform the user about the situation and ask how they want to proceed."},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 还是跳转到了登录页。TK Seller 后台所有页面都需要登录才能访问。\n\n---\n\n## TK 数据获取的选项\n\n| 方式 | 是否可行 | 说明 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| **Seller 后台（需登录）** | ❌ AI 无法自动登录 | 需要手机验证码 |\n| **公开 TK Shop 商品页** | ✅ 可以 | 抓取公开产品页面 |\n| **第三方数据平台**（EchoTik等） | ✅ 可以 | 有 API 或浏览器访问 |\n| **你手动导出** | ✅ 可行 | 登录后导出 CSV，我来分析 |\n\n---\n\n## 建议尝试\n\n要不我们先测试一下 **1688 的 Skill**？那个是完全可行的，不受登录限制。\n\n或者如果你有 TK 的**已登录 Session/Cookie**，我可以尝试用它来维持登录状态。\n\n你想先试哪个？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776065993329,"responseId":"062bd0c9791ee420d84c9c8b69aac199"}}
