{"type":"message","id":"6731f787","parentId":"0868955b","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:01:45.254Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"成功进入TikTok热卖商品榜页面！我可以看到数据了：\n\n1. 页面标题：\"TikTok 热卖商品榜\"\n2. 可以看到越南市场的商品列表，包含：\n   - 排名\n   - 商品名称\n   - GMV（以美元和越南盾显示）\n   - 点击次数\n   - 点击率\n   - 店铺名称\n\n商品包括：\n1. Samsung Galaxy A17 LTE - $20万~$38万, 0.77万~1.48万点击, 3.1%~6.1%点击率, Happy Phone Mall\n2. iPhone 17 Pro Max 256GB - $11万~$20万, 0.84万~1.56万点击, 4.5%~8.3%点击率, Viettel Store\n3. iPhone 17 Pro Max 256GB - $9万~$18万, 1万~2万点击, 6.2%~12.5%点击率, ShopDunk Store Vietnam\n4. Samsung Galaxy A07 - $5万~$9万, 0.67万~1.27万点击, 1.3%~2.6%点击率, TabletPlaza\n5. iPhone 17 Pro Max 256GB - $5万~$9万, 2万~4万点击, 1.2%~2.2%点击率, F.Studio By FPT\n6. S1 MINI 风扇 - $5万~$8万, 15万~24万点击, 5.0%~8.0%点击率, KY Tech\n\n\n7. Samsung Galaxy A07 4GB/128GB - $4万~$7万, 4181~6797点击, 1.4%~2.2%点击率, TabletPlaza\n8. Tinh Chất Serum Black Ginseng - $4万~$8万, 3万~6万点击, 2.0%~3.6%点击率, LUNYS STORE\n9. Combo 2 Gói Tã Bỉm Quần Bobby Ultra - $4万~$7万\n\n页面能够正常加载数据，总共200页，每个页面显示10条记录。"},{"type":"text","text":"成功进入 **TikTok 热卖商品榜**！页面数据已加载 ✅\n\n我看到越南市场（VN）的数据了：\n\n| 排名 | 商品 | GMV | 点击 | 点击率 | 店铺 |\n|------|------|-----|------|--------|------|\n| - | Samsung Galaxy A17 LTE | $20-38万 | 0.77-1.48万 | 3.1-6.1% | Happy Phone Mall |\n| - | iPhone 17 Pro Max 256GB | $11-20万 | 0.84-1.56万 | 4.5-8.3% | Viettel Store |\n| - | iPhone 17 Pro Max 256GB | $9-18万 | 1-2万 | 6.2-12.5% | ShopDunk Store |\n| - | S1 MINI 风扇 | $5-8万 | 15-24万 | 5.0-8.0% | KY Tech |\n\n**共 200 页，每页 10 条数据**\n\n现在你想：\n1. **提取这些数据** → 我来提取结构化数据\n2. **测试商品机会页面** → 另一个入口\n3. **其他测试**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776067278297,"responseId":"062bd5d05ee59432e5ff4103a86f9983"}}
