{"type":"message","id":"05d95e65","parentId":"8a553399","timestamp":"2026-04-13T09:49:08.036Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-13 17:48:00 GMT+8] Feishu[tts] DM | ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 [msg:om_x100b52fff3cc08a8c22790b0abd0570]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52fff3cc08a8c22790b0abd0570\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-13 17:48 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\n可以，但本机的这个宿主机内存就4个G。\n\n那如果不行的话，那就调整一下Docker的资源配置，让这个容器的内存稍微大一点"}],"timestamp":1776073748030}}
{"type":"message","id":"73be9567","parentId":"05d95e65","timestamp":"2026-04-13T09:49:26.303Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user says their host machine only has 4GB RAM total. If they're running Docker with limited resources, giving 4GB to the container might not leave enough for the host system.\n\nThe recommendation would be:\n1. If host only has 4GB, maybe give container 2-3GB max\n2. Or consider running VibeSurf directly on the host machine instead of in Docker\n\nLet me suggest adjusting Docker memory and also mention the alternative of running directly on host."},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 4GB 宿主机有点紧张，给容器太多会导致系统不稳定。\n\n---\n\n## 建议配置\n\n**Docker 容器内存：1.5GB - 2GB**（不要超过一半）\n\n```bash\n# 停止当前容器\ndocker stop vibesurf\n\n# 重新启动，增加内存\ndocker run -d \\\n  --name vibesurf \\\n  --memory=\"1.5g\" \\\n  --memory-swap=\"2g\" \\\n  --cpus=\"1.5\" \\\n  vibesurfai/vibesurf\n```\n\n---\n\n## 另一个选择：直接在本机安装 VibeSurf\n\n既然宿主机只有 4GB，**不如直接在宿主机上安装 VibeSurf**（不需要 Docker），这样能直接用本机全部资源。\n\nmacOS: `brew install vibesurf` 或下载安装包\nWindows: 下载安装包\n\n---\n\n你想先试哪个方案？\n1. 调整 Docker 资源配置（1.5GB）\n2. 直接在宿主机安装 VibeSurf"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776073748036,"responseId":"062bef14ef92ea4f30dcc8a372392358"}}
