{"type":"message","id":"7a99adaf","parentId":"404ddbc3","timestamp":"2026-04-13T09:51:33.231Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The system only has 3.7GB RAM total, with only 554MB available! And swap is almost completely used (3.9GB used out of 3.9GB). This is a severely resource-constrained system.\n\nThe user should NOT increase Docker memory - there's simply not enough RAM. Increasing container memory would cause OOM kills.\n\nInstead, the better approach would be to run VibeSurf directly on the host (not in Docker) to avoid the overhead, OR we need to accept that heavy pages like TikTok backend won't work reliably in this environment.\n\nLet me inform the user about the actual memory situation."},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 问题更严重了 —— **当前系统资源严重不足**：\n\n| 项目 | 数值 |\n|------|------|\n| 总内存 | 3.7 GB |\n| 已用 | 2.6 GB |\n| **可用** | **仅 554 MB** ⚠️ |\n| Swap | 3.9 GB 已用 99% |\n\n---\n\n## 结论\n\n**不能增加 Docker 内存**，系统已经没有余量了。增加会导致 OOM（内存溢出）。\n\n---\n\n## 建议\n\n1. **换用轻量级方案**：TK 后台不用 VibeSurf，改用第三方数据平台（EchoTik 等）来获取数据\n2. **升级硬件**：如果想流畅使用 TK 后台浏览器，建议至少 8GB 内存的机器\n3. **清理当前环境**：关掉一些不必要的进程，释放内存\n\n---\n\n你更倾向于哪个方向？\n1. 接受 TK 后台无法稳定使用，转向第三方数据平台\n2. 先清理内存，优化当前环境\n3. 其他想法"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776073881183,"responseId":"062bef99697b8d39df0a38f23cf548b0"}}
