{"type":"message","id":"a9e87df1","parentId":"5025f2e3","timestamp":"2026-04-13T09:54:21.079Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-13 17:53:14 GMT+8] Feishu[tts] DM | ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 [msg:om_x100b52ff81df84a4c4e6e6336c40ba9]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52ff81df84a4c4e6e6336c40ba9\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-13 17:52 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\n诶，你说这办法挺不错的。\n\n其实TK后台给到的这些数据可能意义也不大嘛，因为它没有数据平台的这些要详细一点嘛"}],"timestamp":1776074061074}}
{"type":"message","id":"c0dc703d","parentId":"a9e87df1","timestamp":"2026-04-13T09:54:34.572Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is pointing out that maybe TK Seller backend data isn't that useful anyway because third-party data platforms have more detailed data. This is actually a valid point - third-party platforms like EchoTik are specifically designed to provide richer analytics.\n\nLet me think about what data we actually need:\n- TK后台数据：热销榜、销量、GMV 等\n- 第三方数据平台：更详细的达人数据、佣金率、趋势分析、竞品分析等\n\nThe user is suggesting we might not need TK backend at all, and can rely on third-party platforms instead.\n\nThis is actually a good strategic pivot. Let me confirm this line of thinking."},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 说得很对！\n\n---\n\n## 对比\n\n| 数据维度 | TK 后台 | 第三方数据平台（EchoTik等）|\n|----------|---------|---------------------------|\n| 销量 | 有 | 有，且更详细 |\n| GMV | 有 | 有 |\n| 达人带货数据 | ❌ 无 | ✅ 详细 |\n| 佣金率 | ❌ 无 | ✅ 有 |\n| 趋势分析 | 有限 | ✅ 多维度 |\n| 竞品分析 | 有限 | ✅ 完整 |\n| API 支持 | ❌ 无 | ✅ 部分有 |\n\n---\n\n## 结论\n\n**第三方平台数据更全面**，而且它们本身就做了数据聚合，比 TK 后台更适合做选品分析。\n\n---\n\n## 调整后的流程\n\n```\n第三方数据平台（EchoTik/InfluTalk）\n    ↓ 浏览器或 API 获取\n数据汇总 + 评分筛选\n    ↓\n1688 采购数据（VibeSurf）\n    ↓\n飞书 Bitable\n```\n\n这样 **TK 后台就不是必须的**了，VibeSurf 只需要负责 1688 的数据采集。\n\n你觉得这个方向可以吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776074061079,"responseId":"062bf04d2e0b03a011e6a63d90020754"}}
