{"type":"message","id":"14e0e3ea","parentId":"5bc8acfa","timestamp":"2026-04-13T09:56:26.468Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-13 17:55:20 GMT+8] Feishu[tts] DM | ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 [msg:om_x100b52ff96bd78b0c1191027e0bfb14]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52ff96bd78b0c1191027e0bfb14\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-13 17:55 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\n那路径变短了吗？\n\n数据平台找到通过指标筛选出来的这些产品，然后再用图片到1688来搜款，是吗？"}],"timestamp":1776074186464}}
{"type":"message","id":"98455635","parentId":"14e0e3ea","timestamp":"2026-04-13T09:56:43.359Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if the workflow is shorter now - basically: find products through the third-party data platform using indicator filtering, then use image search on 1688 to find similar products. Let me confirm this is the workflow they're describing."},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 对！就是这个路径：\n\n---\n\n## 优化后的流程\n\n```\n第三方数据平台（EchoTik 等）\n    ↓ 筛选：销量↑ + 增长率↑ + 竞争度↓\n找到目标商品\n    ↓\n复制图片\n    ↓\n1688 图片搜索（搜同款）\n    ↓\n找到供应商 → 获取采购价、重量、供应商评分\n    ↓\n利润测算 + 评分\n    ↓\n写入飞书 Bitable\n```\n\n---\n\n## 优势\n\n1. **路径更短** → 只需要 VibeSurf 操作 1688（图搜）\n2. **数据更准** → 第三方平台数据维度更全\n3. **资源要求低** → 1688 页面比 TK 后台轻量得多\n\n---\n\n要我现在用 VibeSurf 演示一下 **1688 图片搜索** 这个环节吗？先找个产品图片跑一遍。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776074186468,"responseId":"062bf0cf607ce9fc36d699e90152545a"}}
